{
  "stem": "12684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that brat was back in the house again, meaning me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I then learned that you should never, never show when you're afraid.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like dogs smell it when you're afraid, people feel it when you're afraid, and then they know they are the top dog or they can do whatever they want.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to leave the apartment because they wanted that all the Jewish people would live in designated houses, which were not together in one complex, but all around the city.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Mother and I lived in one room with one kitchen with all the other people on the floor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was one bathroom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a trying affair, but you make do, as simple as that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How far from where you used to live was this new place?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe-- when you drive it, it's less than seven minutes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When you walk it, it's good over half hour, hour.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] An officer of the SS wanted the apartment and people came to look at the apartment.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since it was a duplex, he wanted it very badly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he even specified what to keep in the apartment, which could not be taken out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to leave until a certain day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The end of-- no, it must have been the end of '41.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yeah, '40, '41.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, I mean, he specified he wanted all these chairs and all this stuff there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to leave it there, no argument.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean in this--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the new place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think four or five.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I knew them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mother didn't know them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were-- I do know there were two brothers, each of them married.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
